This file describes installing Layer Manager software
on various platforms. This document is largely centered
around the GENIVI baseline so it will mostly have a 
description that is relevant to the baseline. It won't
cover other platforms.

Installing on OMAP 3 with Ubuntu OS
---
Here are the details of the particular target;
uname: Linux ubuntu 2.6.38-8-omap #42-Ubuntu Mon Apr 11 12:45:46 UTC 2011 armv7l armv7l armv7l GNU/Linux
cmake: cmake version 2.8.3
dbus:

These should all be consider pre-requisites;

1. cmake (build tool)
2. dbus
3. libdus-1-dev
4. xserver-xorg-core
5. libgles1-sgx-omap3
6. libgles2-mesa libgles2-mesa-dev
7. libxcomposite-dev
